      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation that must be seen to be appreciated. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating, and is entirely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats from the start. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the heads-up display, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by the dealership. It currently sits on a fresh set of Michelin tires and has recently undergone a full preventative maintenance service, including all fluid flushes. Included in the sale are both original key fobs, the complete owner's manual set, and a detailed folder of all maintenance records. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did when it first rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
